schools.name: Southern School of Energy and Sustainability

data.description: Welcome to this elegant 55+ home that offers three bedrooms, three full baths, and an inviting loft/flex space. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the exquisite custom trim work, designer light fixtures and nuanced decor that adds a touch of sophistication and charm to every room. The 3-season porch with the extended patio and Eze Breeze windows is a place where you can enjoy the fresh air and beautiful views throughout the seasons while being shielded from those pesky insects. Equipped with high-end SS appliances, single bowl SS sink, and granite countertops, the European inspired kitchen effortlessly combines functionality and style while the primary suite impresses with its double tray ceiling and custom closet design. The extra-large garage, ample closet space and floored attic allow for plenty of storage. From community events to fitness centers/pools and social events, Carolina Arbors offers a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and endless possibilities. Convenient to shopping, entertainment, and renowned medical care, offering a great Triangle location. Long days on market, and previous offers no fault of the sellers, inspections or property flaws. Purchase with confidence!
